{"type":"message","id":"d0843bd5","parentId":"dd22bd94","timestamp":"2026-03-26T09:57:30.559Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Exploring PowerShell Commas**\n\nI need to commit with PowerShell, but I'm getting a bit caught up with the use of semicolons. It seems like they play a role in separating commands, but I’m wondering if using them consistently is essential. Is there a certain format that I should follow? I'll need to experiment with it to ensure I'm committing correctly. Actually, maybe I need to double-check the syntax to avoid any issues down the line!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_066c8af42eb67afc0169c50308073881919fee39d659644096\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpxQMKZXxXpAZJUQOj3le2ebkktD3IZXaxObIKLe40HGXyOxFznI254ULrzp2h1W9i1GSfQI0y29c3-pp0FoiXNpHT70OC8gm5ARESpWbwiQ87D5KXTOmtB8ZD_ps9XA_j7-08eAUiTZ-Kt2XJdovwmSqvSRhpJEUOw3l_LDi0nHha2CaAhjZEywonaQNcw92DgSvST-wBj000mcmdGRxSqRhgA-cEOXEpePskBoy7vNJkBZfhrbV5fPT3YbiW_CY2h_lfWSrCZZ2XMNMVILuQHTk5lIw2TbnnmEc5357pN3Wnq1mMylau1onZ00tFtJ7mG8FI7keS_p4_zct43eK_jrAIIhyGwMjaiiSgiWtcTINPa0yrUVUUeeBXQIJHt_79tqFday0hBxg4XMtM42uRw1j__htJsKmb7oUwto-Xhsfo_MSawIl4WFVoIpe89pzVXkwva4ecksImzTMBipGJINwqBB4fAULK0GXAIsmdIaup9gB4VmnbXmMHK_T4Hrn-x-6IG6G8cBCKst5eXoMo-V12vhquRcwgjjnfUv3nnonl_pzisARV-kzmu5zBNSd7tsdUxoGLTdHPaHpW5paco-u2Nc2MhJxBhm2lKNE143Ubsb-581R0ZBPattjXR7xMpYFgKG9xswGzN6lnxXsPaOrfaw8W3f0BC4_fNJZ3jzBXENCerxF9BPj9AQw2xNq8U889n0dEWcGQ5G0apUVEASlU3BeQ9vMe7Q6CQl0PMvLW7lZX24dH_pWMESfFh6dfC2-TfrWWOfj0CLXJtl_x2rWQKYpF44Ae7X5g0qjo6h5J-Lqphmk88ZEsrr7GlsCgOS0QQvmCAQiI4W5-HYZez4AVMq3DTS5O_8Rk98HJi1NlRDU=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Exploring PowerShell Commas**\\n\\nI need to commit with PowerShell, but I'm getting a bit caught up with the use of semicolons. It seems like they play a role in separating commands, but I’m wondering if using them consistently is essential. Is there a certain format that I should follow? I'll need to experiment with it to ensure I'm committing correctly. Actually, maybe I need to double-check the syntax to avoid any issues down the line!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Em đã lưu kiến thức đó vào bộ nhớ làm việc của em rồi. Em commit nốt thay đổi để workspace sạch.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_066c8af42eb67afc0169c5030a8df88191a532fc76fc0ddab5\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ddCpriS73FYAu5RQuU6UPZf8|fc_066c8af42eb67afc0169c5030a9cac8191a9595fc76927afc8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git status --short; git add memory/2026-03-26.md MEMORY.md; git commit -m \"Add Interlink customer support knowledge to memory\"","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":60},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"git status --short; git add memory/2026-03-26.md MEMORY.md; git commit -m \\\"Add Interlink customer support knowledge to memory\\\"\",\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000,\"timeout\":60}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":393,"output":121,"cacheRead":17408,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17922,"cost":{"input":0.0009825,"output":0.001815,"cacheRead":0.004352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0071495}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774519045993}}
