n check the --help option for more details. That way, I can provide an accurate answer based on the user’s inquiry!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"Em xem thêm đúng phần quản lý channel/bot để nói anh khỏi mò.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_066c8af42eb67afc0169ca437d35488191b0a3ba973bce7162\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_uU8HRRhN7dE9G0NsWkPMkV7x|fc_066c8af42eb67afc0169ca437d3e6c81918e304969071a7766","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw channels --help","workdir":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\workspace","yieldMs":8000,"timeout":30},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"openclaw channels --help\",\"workdir\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\admin\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\",\"yieldMs\":8000,\"timeout\":30}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1203,"output":97,"cacheRead":34816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36116,"cost":{"input":0.0030075,"output":0.0014550000000000001,"cacheRead":0.008704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013166500000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774863222720}}
{"type":"message","id":"ba88de7f","parentId":"4bfe24a0","timestamp":"2026-03-30T09:33:54.507Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_uU8HRRhN7dE9G0NsWkPMkV7x|fc_066c8af42eb67afc0169ca437d3e6c81918e304969071a7766","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — The only open-source project where the mascot could eat the competition.\n\nUsage: openclaw channels [options] [command]\n\nManage connected chat channels and accounts\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add           Add or update a channel account\n  capabilities  Show provider capabilities (intents/scopes + supported features)\n  help          Display help for command\n  list          List configured channels + auth profiles\n  login         Link a channel account (if supported)\n  logout        Log out of a channel session (if supported)\n  logs          Show recent channel logs from the gateway log file\n  remove        Disable or delete a channel account\n  resolve       Resolve channel/user names to IDs\n  status        Show gateway channel status (use status --deep for local)\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw channels list\n    List configured channels and auth profiles.\n  openclaw channels status --probe\n    Run channel status checks and probes.\n  openclaw channels add --channel telegram --token <token>\n    Add or update a channel account non-interactively.\n  openclaw channels login --channel whatsapp\n    Link a WhatsApp Web account.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/channels"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5752,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a) — The only open-source project where the mascot could eat the competition.\n\nUsage: openclaw channels [options] [command]\n\nManage connected chat channels and accounts\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add           Add or update a channel account\n  capabilities  Show provider capabilities (intents/scopes + supported features)\n  help          Display help for command\n  list          List configured channels + auth profiles\n  login         Link a channel account (if supported)\n  logout        Log out of a channel session (if supported)\n  logs          Show recent channel logs from the gateway log file\n  remove        Disable or delete a channel account\n  resolve       Resolve channel/user names to IDs\n  status        Show gateway channel status (use status --deep for local)\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw channels list\n    List configured channels and auth profiles.\n  openclaw channels status --probe\n    Run channel status checks and probes.\n  openclaw channels add --channel telegram --token <token>\n    Add or update a channel account non-interactively.\n  openclaw channels login --channel whatsapp\n    Link a WhatsApp Web account.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/channels","cwd":"C:\\Users\\admin\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774863234502}}
{"type":"message","id":"ccbb26b9","parentId":"ba88de7f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T09:34:14.268Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_066c8af42eb67afc0169ca438de1f48191ab6ab1e5d6fd3cf7\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpykOPSzymiudhhxYoTqQ7iVXdilZqRPIFVDlcHquHeftuaQokoMgyyxW99z7KYiOIzWyIPyNug2b46AUVNW_OC_DmrYRgrUWLlz_7OOIy8oRlyLrLv5O4lWzoOBEQa0wSB25tCAzd44kdzoui1Bw9FPjenTGFX28I8qsKSsIPM_eRUAxN1I2bsOf1Gd_LXVlgxbxr85WIZ1VWof07TxlWcScsoB40pcUN3motb39lUWaOcLdK00IV1eQ21EEDDQZ3VGCkMf8vbmIrmWupxgOfY0xubr_vOOBgpkXblllqkMo9VVh1MxEVbQ-LR_Xzt9fsNFXDQqtvF_0Ft9EOh1M42oETlo846cp-7yAaMaekOo_XqZZJUzxIucNwbvNkVnckOjjID9w3qQdIZ1JwnHjQeFGEe2KqtEYXE8v1QtEnQxp-wZeJPxM0PllHpB6dhxG1Vby98m1CpsJdUkDfLToxYSU_jbsLsegoVd8yfjKy8CUC0MDEM_1K5pJJE2DN-XujmGpNwErv4QkQgCIVK4CZ84sn8SnO7A8mgzkWo6qCffEVgqn_9Y4-IcFfBHOsBg0yuYn0MsfdxxEt74AOXMUS7HKF58sapHoEWEgvhQ8qq2UGSHb-2coYub4610uKvOluVz3k5lOH5qH4ZYpQA6CikDWEVqiHWqKYDnqWaqGlYYCjGveXAsimHX8t6AtgHNfII1ujfvOR3vn9LtUgVjr226L1DbdHTW9mOfqFm0lshGI0xVQZBLkhRhy0tEurs0FTJzDBr-8nEX9VWSXEuFhGx_XXAHN7YlgQjjOkwFo8lb5AU0VhWV_amVvKKybbFbRU7zroknecuNOo6H-YkxxP5L8jiP5C4A9fxjREmgfHJWEDfN7itq2H2Thhg19TRCH9XLgl62lMvKz_PsQiPb8c07-9BZF4tUI4o6b91PgzXG1pTnG7xSMYCkDrNdOE_sJWwXYW\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Nếu anh muốn **chuyển sang bot Telegram mới**, cách nhanh nhất là:\n\n1. **Tạo bot mới với BotFather**\n   - vào Telegram nhắn **@BotFather**\n   - dùng lệnh **/newbot**\n   - đặt tên + username\n   - lấy **bot token**\n\n2. **Gắn bot mới vào OpenClaw**\n   Chạy:\n   ```bash\n   openclaw channels add --channel telegram --token <BOT_TOKEN_MOI>\n   ```\n\n3. **Kiểm tra bot đã lên chưa**\n   ```bash\n   openclaw channels status --probe\n   ```\n\n4. Nếu muốn bỏ bot cũ thì xem danh sách rồi remove:\n   ```bash\n   openclaw channels list\n   openclaw channels remove\n   ```\n   hoặc logout/remove account cũ tuỳ cách nó đang được cấu hình.\n\nNếu ý anh là **đổi sang bot mới nhưng vẫn giữ toàn bộ memory/workspace hiện tại**, thì thường chỉ cần **thay channel Telegram/token**, còn memory của em vẫn giữ trong workspace hiện tại.\n\nNếu anh muốn, em có thể làm tiếp cho anh theo 1 trong 2 cách:\n- **cách A:** em hướng dẫn anh từng bước với BotFather\n- **cách B:** anh gửi token bot mới, em gắn luôn vào OpenClaw cho anh.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_066c8af42eb67afc0169ca438fd7fc8191932f35210b07163f\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":431,"output":314,"cacheRead":35968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36713,"cost":{"input":0.0010775000000000001,"output":0.00471,"cacheRead":0.008992,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014779500000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774863234509}}
{"type":"message","id":"fe891d18","parentId":"ccbb26b9","timestamp":"2026-03-30T09:34:16.323Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-30 16:33:42 GMT+7] Exec completed (marine-m, code 0) :: o the default gateway port, then start it. openclaw gateway ... Gateway control via WebSocket. openclaw agent --to +15555550123 --message \"Run summary\" --deliver Talk directly to …\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file C:/Users/admin/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 30th, 2026 — 4:34 PM (Asia/Bangkok) / 2026-03-30 09:34 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774863256319}}
